---
import ScrollDownArrow from '../../ui/ScrollDownArrow.astro';
---

<section id="under-the-hood" class="section-tight pt-12 lg:pt-16">
  <div class="container-x text-center">
    <div class="eyebrow">under the hood</div>
    <h1 id="hero-headline" class="h-display-lg mx-auto mt-3 max-w-[820px]">
      What runs when you call <span class="font-mono" style="font-size: 0.78em; letter-spacing: -0.005em;">agent.run</span>.
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-[560px] text-fg-2" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Most agent products are <span class="hl-soft">a single model in a loop</span>. Ten minutes is fine. Thirty is iffy. An hour usually isn’t happening.
    </p>
    <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-[560px] text-fg-2" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.6;">
      Midsphere isn’t one of those. Below is how each piece is built — and why it had to be.
    </p>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-10 flex justify-center">
      <ScrollDownArrow />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
